Deemos looks back to check if Sharpedge was there.

"Rizopas will be marking our way, we will not get lost. And Horn Drill and
Doom Ice will be at the entrance in case anything wrong happens." Deemos
assured everyone the safety of walking through these tunnels.

"For the dark lord." Shokaract said. He looked around a corner and seen
Vulois with Deemos' three enemies. Testifier looked on at them. He seen the
one, that looked like Technosis again. He stepped back.

"There they are!" Deemos yells. Shokaract fires a missile that explodes,
blasting Technosis, Psuedo, and Atma to the ground...
